    <ol>
      <li>Open <strong>RecordNow!</strong> and record a 10‑second idea. Save it.</li>
      <li>Open <strong>Saved Snips</strong>, expand the row, and review the suggestions.</li>
      <li>Go to <strong>Lyric Book</strong>, set your key, and paste your first verse. Use the palette to try chords.</li>
      <li>Hit <strong>Pomodoro‑Noise!</strong> and choose a 30‑minute sprint. One small thing at a time.</li>
